'''''Death to All Mages''''' was a ballad written by [[Bendoglaer Syndrath]], [[Bard]] of [[Barrowhill]] in the {{YearlinkName|975}}.

{{quote|''In mighty towers they quake with fright<br/>For the man who kills [[mage]]s is out tonight.''|Bendoglaer Syndrath, Bard of Barrowhill}}
